{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/simple-shell-script-for-automating-github-push/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteTitle":"daniel-dev","author":{"name":"Daeyeon Kim","social":{"github":"https://github.com/shaqok","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/daniel-daeyeon-kim/","email":"shaqok8@gmail.com"}},"siteUrl":"https://shaqok.github.io","menuLinks":[{"name":"about","link":"/about"}]}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>This is a post about automating github push command written in bash shell script. This example is based on my github repo, which is for archiving coding problems/solutions.</p>\n<p>My repository has a structure like below:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">└── problem_category_1\n    ├── problem_1\n    │   └── Problem.md\n    │   └── problem_1.js\n    ├── problem_2\n    │   └── Problem.md\n    │   └── problem_2.js\n    │    \n    problem_category_2\n    ├── problem_1\n    │   └── Problem.md\n    │   └── problem_1.js\n    └── problem_2\n        └── Problem.md\n        └── problem_2.js</code></pre></div>\n<p>If I want to solve a problem, I have to create a <code class=\"language-text\">problem</code> directory under <code class=\"language-text\">problem_category</code> and then create <code class=\"language-text\">Problem.md</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">problem.js</code> under <code class=\"language-text\">problem</code>. Also, if <code class=\"language-text\">problem_category</code> doesn’t exist, i.e. I want to solve a new category of problems, I have to add a <code class=\"language-text\">problem_category</code> directory first. And this is how it works:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Find the problem type</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Enter the type of the problem:\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Show the list of the directories</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">ls</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> */\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Read the input</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">read</span> pType\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$pType</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># Control will enter here if $DIRECTORY doesn't exist.</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$pType</span>\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$pType</span> folder is created\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># # Print the statement</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Enter the name of the problem you want to solve:\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Read the input \"problem'</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">read</span> problem\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Replace spaces with underscores</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">problem</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">${problem<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>_}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># # Create a directory for the problem</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$pType</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$problem</span>\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># # Create problem.md and the js file.</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">touch</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$pType</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$problem</span>/Problem.md\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">touch</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$pType</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$problem</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">$problem</span>.js\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Each time you create a script file and try to run it, you will encounter a message saying that the permission to execute the file is denied. To fix this, you have to give permission to this script file:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># +x grants permission to execute\nchmod +x your_script_file</code></pre></div>\n<p>Now, I just have to type the name of the <code class=\"language-text\">problem_type</code> directory and the name of the <code class=\"language-text\">problem</code> that I am going to solve. Hope this helps!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Simple Shell Script for Automating Github Push","summary":"Simple shell script to automate manage files and to push to Github","date":"2022.04.01.","categories":["shell","bash","github"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/5c813/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.jpg","srcSet":"/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/acb6a/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.jpg 886w,\n/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/fce04/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.jpg 1772w,\n/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/5c813/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.jpg 3543w","sizes":"(min-width: 3543px) 3543px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/3af2b/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.webp 886w,\n/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/9434b/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.webp 1772w,\n/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/13e2c/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.webp 3543w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 3543px) 3543px, 100vw"}]},"width":3543,"height":2365}},"publicURL":"/static/a08347b3be49bb8a0be96f47b27c5d21/ilya-pavlov-OqtafYT5kTw-unsplash.jpg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/simple-shell-script-for-automating-github-push/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}